dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Livermore quadrangle, Contra Costa & Alameda Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Livermore, CA1961, DMA 1659 III NE - Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1980." "First printing, February 2006." "Contour interval 20 feet." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
